INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (177,1,'2025-03-12 11:02:28','2025-03-12 11:02:28','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The introduction of free transportation for all students marks a significant step toward enhancing accessibility and reducing financial barriers to education. With unlimited bus fare, students can now commute to and from school, attend extracurricular activities, and access essential resources without the burden of transportation costs. This initiative not only promotes equity by ensuring that all students, regardless of their economic background, have equal opportunities to attend school but also encourages the use of public transportation, contributing to a more sustainable and eco-friendly community. By removing this logistical hurdle, students can focus more on their studies and personal growth, fostering a more inclusive and supportive educational environment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Free Transportation','All students have free unlimited bus fare.','publish','closed','closed','','free-transportation','','','2025-03-20 09:54:23','2025-03-20 09:54:23','',0,'http://fictional-university.local/?post_type=slide&#038;p=177',0,'slide','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (181,1,'2025-03-12 13:28:33','2025-03-12 13:28:33','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our dentistry program recommends eating apples as a natural way to promote oral health. To encourage healthy habits, we are excited to introduce \"Apple Day,\" where students can enjoy free, fresh apples throughout the day. Apples are not only delicious but also help clean teeth, strengthen gums, and stimulate saliva production, which reduces the risk of cavities. This initiative aims to raise awareness about the importance of nutrition in maintaining a healthy smile while providing students with a tasty and nutritious snack. By making apples easily accessible, we hope to inspire lifelong habits that benefit both dental health and overall well-being.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','An Apple a Day','Our dentistry program recommends eating apples.','publish','closed','closed','','an-apple-a-day','','','2025-03-20 09:53:00','2025-03-20 09:53:00','',0,'http://fictional-university.local/?post_type=slide&#038;p=181',0,'slide','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (183,1,'2025-03-12 13:29:51','2025-03-12 13:29:51','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fictional University offers lunch plans for those in need, ensuring that no student has to face hunger while pursuing their education. Through the Free Food initiative, all students have access to nutritious meals at no cost, removing financial barriers and promoting a supportive campus environment. This program not only addresses food insecurity but also fosters a sense of community by ensuring that everyone has the energy and focus needed to succeed academically. By prioritizing students\' well-being, Fictional University demonstrates its commitment to equity, inclusivity, and the holistic development of its student body. Free Food is more than just a meal—it’s a step toward a brighter, more equitable future for all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Free Food','Fictional University offers lunch plans for those in need.','publish','closed','closed','','free-food','','','2025-03-25 10:58:10','2025-03-25 10:58:10','',0,'http://fictional-university.local/?post_type=slide&#038;p=183',0,'slide','',0);
